title: Terminator (1984) Censored - nudity edited out
description:
There're are a lot of good movies out there that I would feel more comfortable watching with my kids in the room if there just wasn't nudity.  It's not like I encourage the other stuff, like violence and cussing, etc., but with kids I think nudity is the line I draw.  So I',m editing movies to cut the nudity out and making them available to anyone else who feels the same way.

Most of the movies I post are taken from yify orversions

The Terminator (1984)- censored for nudity for PG13 Version
